Title: Series: The life of St Antony Abbot
Description: Plate 1: the birth of St Antony upon the intercession of the Virgin to end the sterility of this parents in Egypt. 1597 Etching
Curator's comments: This is the first of 27 etchings (+ title page) depicting the life of St Anthony.There is no indication who compiled the album. The title page described at 1870,0514.3034 was published by Orlandi but it is not clear if he published all the impressions in this volume. A later edition was published by Greuter.
Associated names: Representation of: St Antony of Egypt
